## 💳 Payment Integration (Implemented)

### Overview
Stripe Checkout (hosted payment page) integration. All payment logic is server-side.
Currency is JPY only (zero-decimal). Multi-currency support can be added later via the `currency` column.

---

### New Files & Key Changes

| File | Role |
|---|---|
| `app/Http/Controllers/PaymentController.php` | checkout / webhook / success / cancel |
| `app/Models/Payment.php` | Payment model (updated) |
| `database/migrations/..._create_payments_table.php` | payments table migration |
| `app/Console/Commands/ExpirePendingPayments.php` | Artisan command for expiry |
| `routes/console.php` | Schedule: every minute |
| `routes/web.php` | Payment routes added |
| `app/Http/Middleware/VerifyCsrfToken.php` | Webhook excluded from CSRF |
| `app/Http/Middleware/HandleInertiaRequests.php` | `warning` flash added to shared props |

---

### payments Table Columns

| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `reservation_id` | ULID FK | cascadeOnDelete |
| `payment_method` | string | e.g. `stripe_checkout` |
| `status` | string | pending / paid / canceled / expired / failed |
| `stripe_session_id` | string unique | NOT NULL — set at checkout |
| `stripe_session_url` | string nullable | Used for redirecting to existing session |
| `payment_intent_id` | string nullable unique | Set by webhook on completion |
| `amount` | unsignedInteger | Copied from total_price_yen at checkout |
| `currency` | string(3) default JPY | For future multi-currency support |
| `payment_region` | string(2) nullable | Card issuing country from Stripe |
| `paid_at` | datetime nullable | Set by webhook on completion |

No soft deletes — payments are audit records and must never be deleted.
One reservation can have multiple Payment records (retries after failure/cancel).

---

### reservation_status Values (Updated)

| Status | Meaning |
|---|---|
| `pending` | Reservation created, awaiting payment (slot held) |
| `booked` | Payment confirmed by Stripe webhook |
| `canceled` | Payment expired / user canceled / failed |

Overlap checks count both `booked` and `pending` as occupying the slot.

---

### Payment Flow

```
User clicks "Pay with Stripe" on confirmation page
    ↓ POST → reservations.store
      - Availability check (booked + pending)
      - Create Reservation (status: pending)
      - Redirect to payments.checkout
    ↓ GET → payments.checkout
      - If active pending Payment exists → redirect to existing session URL
      - Re-check availability (with lockForUpdate)
      - Create Stripe Checkout Session (expires_at: +30 min)
      - Create Payment record (status: pending)
      - Redirect to Stripe

Stripe Checkout page (Stripe-hosted)
    ↓ success           ↓ cancel
payments.success    payments.cancel
    ↓                   ↓
reservations.index  Mark payment: canceled
(ok toast)          Reservation stays pending (retry possible)
                    reservations.index (warning toast)

Stripe Webhook → payments.webhook
  checkout.session.completed  → Reservation: booked, Payment: paid
  checkout.session.expired    → Reservation: canceled, Payment: expired
  payment_intent.payment_failed → Payment: failed (reservation stays pending)

Artisan: payments:expire-pending (every minute)
  → Payments pending > 30 min → Payment: expired, Reservation: canceled
```

---

### Guards in checkout()

1. Reservation must belong to current user (abort 403)
2. reservation_status must be `pending` (redirect if booked or canceled)
3. If active pending Payment exists → redirect to existing stripe_session_url
4. Re-check availability with DB lock before creating Stripe session

---

### Session Expiry

- Stripe session `expires_at`: 30 minutes (minimum allowed by Stripe)
- Artisan command runs every minute as backup in case webhook is not delivered
- Both set Payment: `expired` and Reservation: `canceled`

